# RFM Degradome Validation — R Analysis Scripts

**Regulatory Flux Model (RFM): computational validation across independent plant degradome datasets**

This repository contains the R scripts used to classify miRNA–target pairs into RFM regulatory zones (PTD, CR, TD) across three independent degradome datasets, apply the proxy-based RFM adaptation to *Eragrostis curvula*, and generate Figures 6 and 7 of the manuscript:

> Garbus I. (2026). *Degradome Sequencing in Plants: From Cleavage Mapping to Regulatory Flux Modeling.* [Journal name, under review]

---

## Repository structure

```
RFM-degradome-validation/
│
├── 01_RFM_Yan2024.R          # Dataset 1: Arabidopsis floral tissue (Yan et al. 2024)
├── 02_RFM_German2008.R       # Dataset 2: Arabidopsis seedlings (German et al. 2008)
├── 03_RFM_Shin2018.R         # Dataset 3: O. sativa N-starved roots (Shin et al. 2018)
├── 04_RFM_Ecurvula.R         # Proxy-based RFM inference in E. curvula
├── 05_Figures.R              # Figure generation (Figures 6 and 7)
│
├── quantification/
│   ├── RFM_classified.csv              # Merged degradome + RPKM data, Dataset 1
│   ├── rpkm.csv                        # RPKM values from Yan 2024 RNA-seq (TAIR10)
│   └── SRR5713903_counts_transcriptid.txt  # featureCounts output, Dataset 3
│
├── cleaveland/
│   ├── german2008/
│   │   ├── SRR000222_results.txt       # CleaveLand4 output, Dataset 2 library 1
│   │   └── SRR000223_results.txt       # CleaveLand4 output, Dataset 2 library 2
│   └── shin2018/
│       └── SRR5713893_cleaveland_results.txt  # CleaveLand4 output, Dataset 3
│
├── ecurvula/
│   ├── miRNA_abundance_by_family.csv   # sRNA-seq read counts per miRNA family
│   └── transcript_RPKM.csv            # Transcript RPKM per genotype
│
└── RFM_repository/
    ├── results/                        # Output CSVs (generated by scripts)
    └── figures/                        # Output PNGs (generated by script 05)
```

---

## Dependencies

| Software | Version | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| R | 4.3.1 | All scripts |
| ggplot2 | ≥ 3.4.0 | Figures (scripts 01, 05) |
| gridExtra | ≥ 2.3 | Multi-panel figures (script 05) |
| edgeR | 4.10.1 | Differential expression (script 04) |
| CleaveLand4 | 4.5 | Degradome analysis (upstream, bash) |
| STAR | 2.7 | RNA-seq alignment (upstream, bash) |
| featureCounts | 1.6.0 | RNA-seq quantification (upstream, bash) |

Install R packages:
```r
install.packages(c("ggplot2", "gridExtra"))
if (!requireNamespace("BiocManager", quietly = TRUE))
    install.packages("BiocManager")
BiocManager::install("edgeR")
```

---

## Usage

Set `WORK` to the root of this repository in each script (default: current directory):

```r
WORK <- "/path/to/RFM-degradome-validation"
```

Run scripts in order:

```bash
Rscript 01_RFM_Yan2024.R       # Produces RFM_Yan2024_classified.csv
Rscript 02_RFM_German2008.R    # Produces RFM_German2008_classified.csv
Rscript 03_RFM_Shin2018.R      # Produces Dataset3_RFM_Shin2018_classified.csv
Rscript 04_RFM_Ecurvula.R      # Produces RFM_predicted_Ecurvula.csv
Rscript 05_Figures.R           # Produces Figure6 and Figure7 PNGs
```

